dooyit.parser

Class AddParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • dooyit.parser.AddParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserCommons

    public class AddParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParserCommons
    The AddParser class takes in an "add" command input and returns a Command object. It is needed for adding floating tasks, deadline tasks and events. It implements the ParserCommons interface to use the shared constants and methods.
    Author:
    Annabel
